dataObject.name:
Description
This process reflects the automated work of a burger robot in a restaurant environment. It has to take orders from customers and then prepare them.
- Customer must place order - Based on the order, the robot prepares the dishes - Robot always provides status updates for the order - Robot prepares the food and places it on a conveyor belt
